      "description": "Priced to sell, this car is a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable transportation without spending a fortune. It shows clear signs of age and use, and it\u2019s not a showpiece, but it still has plenty of value for the right buyer. An honest fair-condition vehicle that\u2019s ready for someone practical who doesn\u2019t mind a little wear.",
