    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Runs and drives, but this is a poor-condition vehicle that shows heavy wear and should be approached as a project, fixer-upper, or very basic transportation. Expect noticeable cosmetic damage, a tired interior, and signs of age throughout. It has not been preserved or kept in especially nice shape, and a buyer should budget for repairs, cleanup, and deferred maintenance. Best suited for someone who wants an inexpensive car and understands it will need work.",
