    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This is a mint-condition example that presents beautifully inside and out. The paint, body, trim, and interior all show extremely well, with the kind of clean, well-preserved appearance buyers hope to find but rarely do. It has clearly been cared for, not just kept running, and it feels like a car that has been maintained and preserved to a very high standard. Expect a sharp, highly original-looking presentation, a very clean cabin, and the sort of overall condition that makes it stand out immediately from typical used examples. If you want one that needs no excuses and is ready to enjoy, this is that kind of car.",
      "price": 46900.0,
