      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward, and full of potential, this vehicle is a smart choice for a budget-conscious buyer seeking dependable basic transportation or a practical project. It shows clear cosmetic and mechanical wear consistent with its condition, and it is being offered as an honest value with no pretense\u2014just a chance to own a vehicle at an accessible price point. A great fit for someone who appreciates a low-entry-cost purchase and the opportunity to make it their own.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with a bit of character? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great opportunity for someone handy, a first-time buyer on a budget, or anyone wanting a simple project. It\u2019s being sold honestly as-is, and while it shows its age, it still has plenty to offer for the right person. If you want cheap transportation with potential, come take a look \u2014 I\u2019m happy to answer questions and be upfront about it.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with a strong-running engine, smooth-shifting drivetrain, and dependable road manners. Not a show car, but it has honest mechanical character and the kind of straightforward platform that\u2019s easy to live with, maintain, and improve. Great candidate for a daily, backup car, or project you can drive while you sort the details. Priced to move for someone who wants practical transportation with real potential.",
      "price": 5900.0,
