      "description": "Honest, rugged, and full of character, this car has the kind of presence that makes every drive feel a little more real. It\u2019s a budget-friendly ride with plenty of life in its story, perfect for someone who appreciates a machine with grit, soul, and room to make it their own. Whether you need an inexpensive daily, a practical second vehicle, or a project with personality, this one offers a chance to get behind the wheel without breaking the bank.",
